snippet.title: Hana : Hide and seek Chapter 1 & 2 Walkthrough / Playthrough - Let's Play (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Hana : Hide and seek Chapter 1 & 2 By Catowo Horror Game Part 1 to Ending [Microsoft Windows]

You move into the city, away from your family. Luckily you find a cheap goshiwon. Although, the day you move in weird things started to happen. You keep seeing this woman... A woman with long black hair covering her face, scrawny body, with long deformed limbs. And the more you fear it, the stronger it gets. And it won't stop until you're dead... will you survive?

Hana - Hide and seek: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2444210/HANA__Hide_and_seek/
Developer: Catowo
Genres: Horror, RPG
Platforms: Microsoft Windows

0:00 Chapter 1
13:26 Chapter 2
